QuestData.Title: Thunderdrome: Zumonga!
QuestData.Description: Splendidly done! But you'll be fighting more than mere humans!$B$BYour next opponent's a mean one...watch out for his right hook. And his left. I'd be wary of his fists in general.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Return to Katrina Turner at Gadgetzan in Tanaris.
QuestData.CompletionText: Stop wasting my time. Enter and fight!
QuestData.RewardText: Not bad. You've got a ways to go, however.
